data.description: Country home bring your chickens, grow your garden, great area, land is open rural. Close to shopping and schools. Windows and well are 3 years old; water treatment and a/c are 2 years old. Deck next to above ground pool in back yard.  Peace and quiet in your nature setting, close to new William Burgess park. Still affordable in Nassau County. Short drive to freeway, and wildlight shopping or dining.  Home is unique, filled with many possibilities.
